    </div>
    <div class="illustration">
        <img src="插图/02-Embedding坐标系统.svg" alt="坐标系统">
        <div class="illustration-caption">给词语标GPS坐标</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="page">
    <h2>第七章：Vector Database - AI的图书馆</h2>
    <div class="illustration">
        <img src="插图/03-VectorDatabase.svg" alt="Vector Database">
        <div class="illustration-caption">向量数据库</div>
    </div>
    <div class="illustration">
        <img src="插图/03-Vector-Database魔法图书馆.svg" alt="魔法图书馆">
        <div class="illustration-caption">魔法图书馆</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="page">
    <h2>第十一章：API - AI的对话通道</h2>
    <div class="illustration">
        <img src="插图/04-API.svg" alt="API">
